<!--====== ABOUT US PART START ======-->
<section class="about-us-3-area pb-130">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-end">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-8">
                <div class="about-us-content">
                    <span class="section-subtitle">About Us</span>
                    @* <h3 class="title">We Support Production and Distribution</h3> *@
                    <p>
                        Wami Agro Limited is a Ghana-based agritech company working hard to turn smallholder farmers into stewards of high-production, yet sustainable land.
                        Founded in March 2020, WamiAgro provides input credit, access to fair trade markets and prices, and education that increases knowledge and resilience among farmers, thereby reducing shocks to supply chains and providing a steadier source of income to thousands of families.
                        With a network of over 14,000 farmers across 6 regions in Ghana, WamiAgro supports the production and distribution of rice, maize, soya beans, sorghum, vegetables, and root tubers.
                        We provide quality and wholesome produce to FMCGs, Bulk Food Distributors, Animal Feed Processors, and Food Service Businesses within and beyond Ghana. We guarantee traceability of all produce sold.
                    </p>
